        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Reda Lemeden</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Interface Designer, 
              <a target="_blank" href="http://thoughtbot.com">Thoughtbot</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm an interface designer building iOS and Rails apps at <a href="http://thoughtbot.com/" target="_blank">thoughtbot</a> in Stockholm. I write on <a href="http://coding.smashingmagazine.com/author/reda-lemeden/" target="_blank">Smashing Magazine</a>, <a href="https://www.google.com/#bav=on.2,or.r_cp.r_qf.&fp=24455ae55976f30f&q=reda+lemeden+site:robots.thoughtbot.com&safe=active" target="_blank">Giant Robots</a>, and my own <a href="http://kaishinlab.com/articles/" target="_blank">blog</a>. I co-authored <a href="http://neat.bourbon.io/" target="_blank">Neat</a> and I'm currently maintaining it. Follow me on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/kaishin" target="_blank">Twitter</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


